"yes" is a very important command in the linux system which are used
to create file of large size (in GB's) in seconds.

Example of this command is :
yes "hello" > hello.txt

Use CTRL+C after 10 to 20 seconds and see the size of the file hello.txt 
located in the current working directory.

Note : Run for a long time it may fill up your entire HDD Space very Quickly. 
